Apple is expected to announce the iPhone 17 series during its usual fall event, which may also see the debut of <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/04/18/airpods-pro-3-upgrades-worth-waiting-for/">third-generation AirPods Pro</a>.<br/>
